messages.message: I am trying to extract the birthdate from a passport and I got an interesting answer from the model after I toggled the switch complex prompt (with the intention to add some formatting)
I just got it, the answer is 5, is referring to the numbering on the passport, date of birth is field number 5 on the passport
This is also a remarkable result

Hopefully my stumbling through AI hub gives an idea of what uneducated users might experience :slightly_smiling_face:

I removed the formatting request and now it is coming back with better results. Perhaps this is all not so relevant anymore with the new version allowing to do formatting after extraction...
